commitResults.messageTitle: Rename the chatbot, implemented greeting of chatbot and also exiting of the chatbot

commitResults.messageBody:
The name of the chatbot is now Tako.
The name is changed to make the chatbot unique to myself

The chatbot can now greet the user and exit.
This is to allow the user to know that they enter and exit the chatbot successfully.

The chatbot will echo the command given by the users.
If the command given is 'bye', the chatbot will exit.

Chatbot can now store text given by the user
If the user types "list", it returns all the text stored by the chatbot
Task.java is added so that the function of marking and unmarking of task can be done in a more natural way.
